title.rendered: Trading Team gathers for their annual meet

content.rendered:
TTE Trading team got together for the annual sales meeting to share strategy for the new year. Meeting for brunch at the elegant Mint Leaf of London, Dubai. Team members from the Trading Division enthusiastically shared insights gained over the past months across various product categories – HVAC equipment & solutions, Refrigeration equipment & solutions, VFDs, HVACR controls & consumables, copper coils and tubes, HVAC ducts & accessories, Advanced Metering Solutions etc.

Dilip Sharma, Executive Vice President of Technical & Trading Est. (TTE) thanked the Trading team, who under the leadership of Roshan Samuel, Associate Vice President had a successful year, surpassing targets and showing growth across all areas of the division.
